            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23716204/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23716204/" class="">第19页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/14408491/" class=" " title="三献茶六文钱">三献茶六文钱</a>
                (看书是最正经的犯罪)
              
